data.description: This home is nestled near the heart of Colusa, CA, presents an extraordinary opportunity for those seeking a perfect blend of space, style, and modern amenities. Spread across two lots totaling nearly half an acre, this property offers an expansive and private living experience. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, the residence is thoughtfully designed with two large living rooms, creating an ideal setting for entertaining both indoors and outdoors. The home exudes warmth with a wood-burning stove and fireplace, providing a cozy ambiance during colder evenings. The large enclosed patio extends the living space, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. A standout feature is the master bedroom's exclusive access to the backyard, enhancing convenience and privacy. Noteworthy upgrades include a fully owned solar system, an investment that reflects a commitment to sustainable living. Over the last two years, the property has seen a large investment in upgrades, encompassing a new shower, AC unit, flooring throughout, and a modern stove. This turn-key ready home boasts numerous other enhancements, creating a seamless transition for its next fortunate owner to enjoy a contemporary and comfortable lifestyle.
